====Usage notes====
In standards of Hong Kong, Japan and Taiwan, the {{zh-l|*人}} component in the lower left of {{lang|zh|幾}} touches but does not cross the horizontal stroke in the {{zh-l|*戈}} component. In standard of Mainland China, the top of the {{lang|zh|人}} component crosses over the horizontal stroke in the {{lang|zh|戈}} component.

